We stuck to the decision of Guide Alandara and stayed in the King room. For the next two hours Peritus and a few others occupied the queen room. They were able to kill the queen in her room with minimal loses as she spawned. Two hours later when the queen again spawns they are not so lucky and wiped out. We moved in, finished her off and helped Peritus with CR by bringing them to the king room. A short time later we killed the king when he spawned, let Peritus know we were going and we left the zone.<br>
